@startuml
title Authenticated Patient Request to Staff Review
actor Patient
participant "Clinic System" as System
participant "JSON Store" as Store
actor "Staff (Doctor/Admin)" as Staff

Patient -> System: Login with demo patient account
System --> Patient: Patient dashboard
Patient -> System: Submit appointment request
System -> System: Validate required fields and safety boundary
alt safety violation
  System --> Patient: Administrative-scope rejection
else valid request
  System -> Store: Store as Pending Review
  System -> System: Recalculate conflict flags for active slots
  System --> Patient: Request saved with current status
end

Staff -> System: Login with doctor/admin account
System --> Staff: Staff dashboard
Staff -> System: View shared queue
System -> Store: Load visible appointments
System --> Staff: Appointment queue with conflict flags
Staff -> System: Confirm or cancel appointment
System -> Store: Update status and review note
System -> System: Recalculate conflict flags
Patient -> System: Refresh own appointment list
System --> Patient: Updated status visible
@enduml
